<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id79c3748e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s3708"><num value="3708">§ 3708.</num><heading> Reservation of right to amend or repeal chapter</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">The Congress expressly reserves the right to repeal or amend this chapter at any time.</p>
